high_descs: Turn right and go across the room to the counter.
Pick up the knife from the counter.
Cut the apple on the counter.
Turn left, head to the coffee maker and look up at the cabinet.
Put the knife in the cabinet above the counter.
Turn around and go back to the counter with the sliced apple.
Pick up a slice of apple.
Head to the microwave on the left.
Put the apple in the microwave, cook it and pick it back up.
Turn left and head to the sink.
Put the slice of apple in the right side of the sink.
anns.task_desc: Put a cooked slice of apple in the sink.

high_descs: Turn right and go across the kitchen to the counter with the microwave on top.
Pick up the gray knife on the counter.
Cut the yellow apple on the counter into three parts.
Turn left and go to the front of the left cabinet above the coffee machine.
Place the gray knife inside the left cabinet.
Turn right and go back to the counter with the cut apples on top.
Pick up one piece of the apple from the counter.
Move over left to the microwave on the counter.
Remove the apple from the microwave after heating it.
Turn around and go to the sink on the right.
Place the apple piece in the sink next to the lettuce.
anns.task_desc: Put a heated apple piece in the sink.

high_descs: Turn right and walk across the room to face the knife on the counter.
Pick up the knife on the counter.
Cut the apple on the counter into three pieces.
Turn left and step forward to face the cabinet above the coffee maker.
Place the knife in the cabinet above the coffee maker.
Turn around and walk forward to face the apple on the counter.
Pick up a piece of apple on the counter.
Take a step to the left to face the microwave.
Heat the piece of apple in the microwave and remove it.
Turn left to face the sink.
Place the apple piece in the right side of the sink.
anns.task_desc: To heat a piece of apple plus place it in the sink.
